{"tid":1231550,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一定要逼林鄭取消\"暴動\"說法","createTime":"2019-06-16T13:06:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T13:41:27.000Z","uid":245238,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"19c61dad76f8a0f4d60f02322f316b0d5307efd0","tid":1231550,"uid":245238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:06:24.000Z","msg":"2016年旺角魚革被定為暴亂。<br />\n<br />\n「本土民主前線」前發言人梁天琦除承認一項襲警罪，經審訊後再被裁定一項暴動罪成，判監6年；黃家駒承認一項暴動罪，判監3年半；盧建民經審訊後被裁定一項暴動罪成，判監7年，是判刑最重的被告。「本土民主前線」成員黃台仰和李東昇逃至德國，並獲批難民庇護資格。<br />\n<br />\n如果今次運動定性為暴動，有份參加人士被清算既話，後果可想而知? <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一定要逼林鄭最消除暴動說法!!!!!!!</span></span>"},{"pid":"c6b3a293037e10009390df075fc1410fe9625638","tid":1231550,"uid":186152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:07:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9e0f0b61a1f2dff6ab1243eb6b1d98d5211348b","tid":1231550,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:07:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc9790de11231fca85cc008719ec9469efa26995","tid":1231550,"uid":245238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c6b3a293037e10009390df075fc1410fe9625638","tid":1231550,"uid":186152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:07:05.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:07:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf4fb51eae5a95f8aae45663203489af4b0eadfe","tid":1231550,"uid":219211,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:08:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"643f7ead4737c00802e8e1be27d5e86594dacd59","tid":1231550,"uid":223468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:13:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ea417f98fc5e214ec2e2c937145e0dd1355c058","tid":1231550,"uid":245238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:17:09.000Z","msg":"根據&lt;公安條例&gt;254章<br />\n暴動<br />\n(1)如任何參與憑藉第18(1)條被定為非法集結的集結的人破壞社會安寧，該集結即屬暴動，而集結的人即屬集結暴動。  (由1970年第31號第12條修訂)<br />\n(2)任何人參與暴動，即犯暴動罪 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)一經循公訴程序定罪，可處監禁<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">10</span></span>年；及<br />\n(b)一經循簡易程序定罪，可處第2級罰款及監禁<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">5年</span></span>。"},{"pid":"8030885385ee180150972e7c29496ffa66f19092","tid":1231550,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:20:52.000Z","msg":"炒左出「暴動」條友"},{"pid":"42761ac48d7e5b52164145e77639f6c500299a18","tid":1231550,"uid":18552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:41:27.000Z","msg":"依樣係一定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個都不能少<br />\n無人係暴徒<br />\n所有都係愛香港嘅人"}]}